title: Vicious 2x07 Finale Special 2016
description:
Vicious Series Finale. Airs June 19, 2016.


Vicious returns for an hour-long special series finale, charting a year in the life of our beloved characters. Freddie (Ian McKellen) and Stuart (Derek Jacobi) are back, joined as ever by Violet (Frances de la Tour), Ash (Iwan Rheon), Penelope (Marcia Warren) and Mason (Philip Voss).

In spring, Freddie and Stuart attempt to hide their recently gained inheritance. Violet has financial troubles after her recent divorce and Ash struggles to meet his rent. Signs of Freddie and Stuartâ€™s expenditure soon threatens the pretense as their home is overrun with guests.

In summer, it's Freddie's birthday party and an unexpected card arrives. Stuart prepares a very special present, Violet has a surprising announcement, and Ash and Penelope share a secret.

In autumn, Ash arrives at Freddie and Stuart's flat with news, whilst in winterthe gang gather 'round at Christmas to experience Freddieâ€™s latest acting job.Vicious is back for one final hurrah, and it's as ferociously funny and heartfelt as ever
